entries.outputEnglish: So tell me more about your pain. I saw you last week, and there was pain on the right side, correct? Have the medications I gave you improved it?
It's a bit better, but I still have some pain. I don't understand, sometimes there's no pain, and sometimes the pain comes suddenly, and I hear a cracking sound from the knee.
Maybe we should increase the dose of the painkiller, what do you think?
